Paper: hep-th/9902130

Date: 1999-02-18

Title: Mass and Decay Spectra of the Piecewise Uniform String

Authors: I. Brevik, A. A. Bytsenko, and A. E. Goncalves

Comments: 7 pages, LaTex, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B453 (1999) 217-221

Mass and decay spectra are calculated for quantum massive excitations of apiecewise uniform bosonic string. The physical meaning of the criticaltemperatures characterizing the radiation in the decay of a massive microstatein string theory is discussed.